####################################################
##  Update information for NConf 1.2.6 to 1.2.7   ##
####################################################

##------------------------------------------------##
##       Changes to the NConf configuration       ##
##------------------------------------------------##
Added:
- Deployment module
  To merge your old deployment or setting up the deployment, please read the online documentation
  http://dev.nconf.org/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=nconf:help:documentation:modules:deployment:main
 


The following configuration option(s) have been removed:
- CONF_DEPLOY_URL
- CONF_DEPLOY_USER
- CONF_DEPLOY_PWD

optional: new constant DEBUG_GENERATE [1-5]

##------------------------------------------------##
##              Additional changes                ##
##------------------------------------------------##

New files generated: host_dependencies.cfg, service_dependencies.cfg 
Files not generated anymore: extended_host_info.cfg, extended_service_info.cfg


Security bug in 'call_ajax.php'
- Please remove this file from your nconf/ directory
- a more secure file handler was implemented ('call_file.php')

####################################################
##           End of update information            ##
####################################################
